Before breaking his arm, Cam could type 9 words per minute * 5 minutes = <<9*5=45>>45 words in 5 minutes.
After breaking his arm, Cam could type 6 words per minute * 5 minutes = <<6*5=30>>30 words in 5 minutes.
The difference is that he can type 45 - 30 = <<45-30=15>>15 more words before he broke his arm than after.
